OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776798670
OL,3,CPeatland restoration stops wildfire
OL,4,Cfrom destroying nature reserve
OL,6,FA wildfire that broke out at a
OL,7,Fprotected nature reserve was
OL,8,Fsuccessfully halted by recent
OL,9,Fconservation work to protect
OL,10,Fpeatlands, experts have confirmed.
OL,12,FConservationists say the blaze at
OL,13,FHighfield Moss, near Wigan, on
OL,14,FThursday, 16 April, could have been a
OL,15,Fpotential disaster for the site's rare
OL,16,Fwildlife and nature.
OL,18,FBut the Lancashire Wildlife Trust says
OL,19,Fthe fire was stopped in its tracks by
OL,20,Fits "rewetting" system designed to
OL,21,Fprotect the peatland.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
