PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776798670
OL,3,CPeatland restoration stops wildfire
OL,4,Cfrom destroying nature reserve
OL,6,FThe charity, who help protect wildlife
OL,7,Fand wild places across the North West,
OL,8,Frevealed that "bunding" - a series of
OL,9,Flow earth banks designed to trap water
OL,10,F- acted as a natural firebreak,
OL,11,Fpreventing the flames from spreading.
OL,13,FThe trust also said the reserve's
OL,14,Fsphagnum moss, which plays a crucial
OL,15,Frole in carbon storage and flood
OL,16,Fmanagement, was "relatively unscathed".
OL,18,FExperts say this is due to the plant's
OL,19,Funique ability to hold up to 20 times
OL,20,Fits own weight in water.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
