CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776798670
OL,3,CPeatland restoration stops wildfire
OL,4,Cfrom destroying nature reserve
OL,6,F"It's a major win for the project,"
OL,7,Fsaid a spokesperson for the Lancashire
OL,8,FWildlife Trust. "It proves that
OL,9,Feffective peatland restoration isn't
OL,10,Fjust good for the climate; it's a
OL,11,Fvital tool in reducing the impact of
OL,12,Fwildfires."
OL,14,FAccording to the trust, Highfield Moss
OL,15,Fis recognised as one of the best
OL,16,Fremaining examples of a lowland raised
OL,17,Fmire in the region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
