PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776798670
OL,3,CPeatland restoration stops wildfire
OL,4,Cfrom destroying nature reserve
OL,6,FRecently designated as part of the
OL,7,F"King's Series" of National Nature
OL,8,FReserves, the site is a sanctuary for
OL,9,Frare plants like cranberry and cross-
OL,10,Fleaved heath.
OL,12,FConservationists have warned that the
OL,13,Fsite remains fragile and has urged the
OL,14,Fpublic to be vigilant.
OL,16,FThey have asked visitors to not light
OL,17,Fbarbecues or open fires, to dispose of
OL,18,Fcigarette ends responsibly and to take
OL,19,Flitter home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
